      "Notes": "Modernized 2026-07-05 per SCADA_2026_ICON_STYLE_GUIDE_V2.md: decomposed from a single legacy raster (asset-97) into 2 native-vector parts (panel, header bevel). Triangle and the 2 fans were split out to their own components (Triangle.sep, VentilateurPale.sep) so each can carry independent runtime state events - ScadaElement.Events is per scene object, not per embedded Part. Legacy raster kept in Assets[] for provenance, no longer referenced. Intended composition: place Condenseur.sep, then Triangle.sep and 2x VentilateurPale.sep on top at their original relative positions (triangle at X=60,Y=170 size 79x45; fans at X=8,Y=78 and X=97,Y=78, size 93x93 each, all relative to the condenser's own 199x216 origin)."
    },
